f\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61692c7e93719fd7fc524a565b5c46206e9a8d51","tid":2450753,"uid":153892,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T12:03:17.000Z","msg":"我都明呢種感覺，身邊既知心好友其實我都好信得過，但我亦好少真係將自己最內心既感受或者struggle講畀佢地聽，唔係因為信唔過佢地或者驚佢地點諗我，而係因為真係太熟所以唔知點解講唔出口，通常都係點到即止，女朋友又係唔會想同佢講呢啲，可能又係唔想將自己最赤裸既一面show晒出黎。<br />\n<br />\n19年之後無論社會同疫情都搞到自己情緒起伏好大，原本有既情緒問題都好似嚴重咗，所以就開始有個念頭想識個soulmate, 由零開始做朋友，不過一直都係諗無實行，一來講得係soulmate 都係想搵異性傾（兩個男人傾心底話有少少老尷），但自己有另一半一來唔方便。同埋又感覺好似會會畀人覺得有企圖想借呢樣嘢識女仔。所以暫時都係諗only。月頭開始餵下屋企附近既流浪貓，都可以令個人放鬆少少，呢個年頭人係信唔過，太多敏感嘢太多social norms要注意，我寧願信隻貓好過，至少佢聽唔明我我聽唔明佢，夠晒安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22afe307af81d1c2ee7c73f7e1f23b313504e618","ti